  "text": "[TO BE PUBLISHED IN THE GAZETTE OF INDIA, EXTRAORDINARY, PART II, SECTION 3, SUB-SECTION (i)] Government of India Ministry of Finance (Department of Revenue) New Delhi, dated the 28 th July, 2011 Notification No. 18 /2011 -Central Excise (N.T) G.S.R. 580(E). - In exercise of the powers conferred by section 62 of the Finance Act, 2011 ( 8 of 2011), the Central Government hereby appoints the 1 st day of August, 2011, as the date on which, the provisions of the said section shall come in to force. [F. No. 354/151/ 2011 - TRU] (Raj Kumar Digvijay) Under Secretary to the Government of India -- 1 of 1 --",
